public class PaymentPopup
extends CustomActivity

The Activity PaymentPopup is launched when user proceed for the payment of Taxi he/she want to book. Currently it will be launched when user tap on middle button located at the bottom of the Map screen. It will also launched when user click on Reserve button in Search dialog. You must customize and enhance this as per your needs.
